Tera Caldwell
Weapon type: Greatsword
Crystal Color: Red
Spheres: B C E

Skill 1: Full Swing
 2-hit AoE Melee BRV attack.
 Inflicts [Crush] on all targets for 4 turns.
 Uses: 5
15cp: Lumber Axe
 +Increases BRV potency
 +Extends base duration of [Crush] by 4 turns
 +Grants ATK Up (40%) to self for 6 turns
c.55: Full Swing Extend
 +Becomes a 5-hit AoE Melee BRV+HP attack
 +HP Damage dealt is split evenly
 +Allows for 180% Stolen BRV overflow
 +Recovers HP to self based on HP damage dealt (30%, up to 20% max HP)

[Crush]: DEF Down (40%), BRV Damage Taken Up (20%)
         HP Recovery Down (50%)

Skill 2: Eternal Flame
 Removes active [Eternal Flame].
 Sets [Eternal Flame] on target.
 Uses: 3
35cp: Solar Axe
 +Grants BRV to party based on own INT BRV (150%)
 +Increases BRV damage dealt with [Eternal Flame]'s trap attack
 +Adds a BRV gain effect (50% INT BRV) before [Eternal Flame]'s BRV hits
c.60: Skill2 Extend
 +Adds 3 uses
 +Triggers a 3-hit Melee BRV+HP attack
 +Adds a Max BRV Down (20%) effects to [Eternal Flame]
  When using [Eternal Flame]'s trap attack:
 +Reduces target's BRV by 1/2 before BRV hits
 +Becomes a 3-hit Fire Melee BRV+HP attack
 +Increases HP recovered based on HP damage dealt (+10%)
 +Raises HP recover cap (+10%)
 
[Eternal Flame]: Triggers a 1-hit Fire Melee BRV+HP attack at the beginning of the target's turn.
                 Heals party based on HP damage dealt (10% HP damage, 10% max HP)
                 BREAK status inflicted with this attack will not delay target
 
EX: Double Trouble
 +Equips EX ability Big Burn
 8-hit AoE Fire Melee BRV+HP attack.
 HP damage dealt is split evenly.
 Allows for 150% Stolen BRV overflow.
 Grants [Striker] to self for 6 turns.
 Inflicts Fire Resistance Down and [Target Lock] on all targets for 6 turns.
 Recast: Normal
  -LB1: Increases BRV damage dealt by 10%
  -LB2: Increases recast speed of Big Burn by 20%
  -LB3: Enemy attacks will not reduce HP below 1 while HP is at least 50% of MAX
 EX+: Increases recast speed of Big Burn by 10%
      Greatly increases BRV potency
      Allows for 180% Stolen BRV overflow
  -LB1: Raises ATK (60%) and Max BRV (80%)
  -LB2: At Quest Start:
        -Grants [Striker] to self for 6 turns
        -On first turn:
         -Does not consume use count
         -No Action Delay
         -Does not increase turn count
         -Decreases Friend Support and Summon action count
  -LB3: Becomes a 6-hit AoE Fire Melee BRV+HP attack, triggered twice.
        Greatly increases BRV potency
        Heals party based on HP damage dealt (30% HP damage, 25% max HP)
        Full Swing use +1 after use (up to initial value)
        Turns BRV Attack to BRV Attack+ while party's HP >= 50%
        Turns BRV Attack to BRV Attack++ when any party member's HP =< 50%
        Turns HP Attack to HP Attack+ while party's HP >= 50%
        Turns HP Attack to HP Attack++ when any party member's HP =< 50%

[Striker]: Self: ATK Up (50%), Fire Enchant (20%), HP Damage Conversion (30% of HP damage taken is blocked and converted into BRV gain)
           Party: HP Regen (12% max HP), BRV Damage Taken Down (50%)
BRV Attack+: 4-hit Fire Melee BRV attack.
             Grants BRV to party based on own INT BRV (150%)
HP Attack+: 3-hit Fire Melee BRV+HP attack.
            Grants BRV to party based on HP damage dealt (30%)
BRV Attack++: 3-hit Fire Melee BRV attack.
              Restores HP to party based on BRV damage dealt (50% BRV damage, 15% max HP)
HP Attack++: 2-hit Fire Melee BRV+HP attack.
             Restores HP to party based on HP damage dealt (50% HP damage, 15% max HP)

LD: Dragon Claw
 +Equips LD ability Dragonheart
 8-hit Fire Melee BRV+HP attack.
 Deals 50% splash HP damage to non-targets.
 Allows for 180% Stolen BRV overflow.
 Sets [Target Lock] on all targets for 6 turns.
 Grants 1 stack of special effect [Sanctuary] to self.
 Uses: 2
  -LB1: Raises own Max BRV, Attack by 20%
        Increases BRV damage dealt by 10%
  -LB2: Raises own Max BRV, Attack by 20%
        Grants an extra stack of [Sanctuary] on use
  -LB3: Raises own Max BRV, Attack by 20%
        Adds 1 use
Board Passive: LD Extend
 +Becomes a 6-hit Fire Melee BRV+HP attack, followed by a 4-hit Fire Melee BRV+HP attack
 +Deals 50% HP damage to non-targets on first HP attack, and 50% TOTAL HP damage to non-targets on second HP attack
 +Increases BRV potency

[Sanctuary]: When any party member's HP falls below 10%:
             -Enemy attacks will not reduce HP below 1
             -Enemy attacks will not reduce BRV below 1
             -Restores party's HP (50% Max HP)
             -Grants BRV to party based on individual Max BRV (50%)
             -Removes 1 stack of [Sanctuary]
